{"tid":695579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆破玩假的？ 美國情報網站：北韓核試場仍可修復使用","createTime":"2018-06-09T10:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T11:40:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a7d4ed6ca6c26a3b1642245e60e2180e36868e","tid":695579,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"爆破玩假的？ 美情報網站：北韓核試場仍可修復使用<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php7MYs5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php7MYs5E.jpg&h=7084430a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓上月24日爆破豐溪里核子試驗場。（路透）<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕眾所矚目的川金會將於12日在新加坡舉行，為重申無核化決心，北韓當局上月24日在外媒面前爆破豐溪里核子試驗場，被視為北韓方面給出的棄核保證之一，但美國情報網站8日公布的監測報告卻顯示，當時爆炸僅爆破坑道入口，部分坑道深處可能完好無損，未來略經修復便可再度使用。<br />\n<br />\n專門關注北韓問題的美國情報網站「北緯38度」（38 North）指出，根據北韓對外媒展示的平面地圖，相關人員在豐溪里核子試驗場內部3條隧道中架設炸藥，炸毀支撐結構，導致通道出入口完全崩塌。然而，該網站進一步分析相關照片，推測內部應完好無損，若由內而外進行修復，並不需要太長時間便可恢復運作。<br />\n<br />\n「北緯38度」進一步表示，核試驗場出入口均已因爆破而封閉，北韓若欲重啟，地面上的活動勢必遭衛星記錄，該網站因而懷疑，豐溪里核試場北面恐另有一條隱藏坑道，北韓可透過該通道派遣人員及機具進入試驗場內部，由地面下施工維修坑道，進而使試驗場恢復<br />\n運作。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpbKsfDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpbKsfDa.jpg&h=b44c444d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓在通道出入口裝設炸藥炸毀支撐結構。（擷取自北緯38度）<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453065&d=Wt0jbW76SMb%2FhzjzdAk9Xx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=94590828\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453065&h=16f47206\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453065</a>"},{"pid":"f168f4398702dc98c2bbe58e5d8b25af98aa2f1b","tid":695579,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"信金仔果個都on9"},{"pid":"cb3adee1501e7149a8c6e80c527cc9eab94123a3","tid":695579,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"金仔無可能放棄幾十年努力成果核武"},{"pid":"6716fd6ad95fa3cb29f4954489658f0ec4e97b87","tid":695579,"uid":170733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"金侵會之你有張良計我有過牆梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470ded64d272709286c5209918d63c18fb3e19ba","tid":695579,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"信放棄核武果個白癡，用幾十年心血先整到咁易唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d28b6d11b4a94de05db8e6c07dbcaa62446a45a","tid":695579,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"咩事又翻炒4 月啲新聞 ?"},{"pid":"bfca39fb98c1ce867cccaa9f4354e5ca358973e0","tid":695579,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53a1ccef4c12139e68d07ed985f3ab1a50533878","tid":695579,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"085f7a637db3d6082840d1865a3971f5f3cdf2c5","tid":695579,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}